@node "History" "History"

 Changes since v1.2b2 (v1.2)
 ---------------------------
 * Changed number of connections the unregistered version allows.
 * Stacksize for external commands can be changed.
 * External commands will now find commands in all paths (added with 'path').
 * Reintroduced delay before banner is displayed, since it was causing
   problems on some systems.
 * Some text of your own choice can now be shown in menus instead of the
   function key commands.
 * Added the bbs name to window titles.
 * Fixed lost screen-title bug.
 * New keywords: ACTIVATEWIN, WINDOWTOFRONT, MRC_BUSY2
 * New rexx-command: TRIMLOG
 * All AKAs will be saved to the log now.
 * Fixed the "long filenames" problem with Hydra (thanks to Dominique Simon).


 Changes since v1.2b1 (v1.2b2)
 -----------------------------
 * New keyword ONCLOSEWINDOW to control behaviour if you click on the close
   window gadget.
 * Added missed 'alias' keywords to GConfig.
 * Hydra xfer window now fits on screens only 640 pixels wide with topaz 8
   font.
 * Settings help now also finds the guide if the path is relative to the
  current directory.
 * Fixed bug for node-requester '<<' button.
 * Address parsing functions are much stricter now.
 * Incorporated HydraCom rev 7 changes into GotchaHydra, and replaced some
   ANSI functions with own routines.


 Changes since v1.1 (v1.2b1)
 ---------------------------
 * New tool: GConfig
   Complete GUI driven configuration tool that can load and save configs, get
   them from running Gotchas, set configs for running Gotchas and has built
   in help (via Gotcha.guide)
 * Added 'Settings' menu to Gotcha. All settings that can be changed at
 * runtime can now be configured via GUI.
 * Current setting can be saved.
 * Major speed up for GList.
 * GList keyword order is no longer important.
 * Special configs can now be set depending on nodelist flags
 * Added CALLERID keyword
 * Fixed memory loss
 * Fixed high CPU usage when ARexxSender Listview is open
 * Added 'Extra' functions to gotcha.library


 Changes since v1.0 (v1.1)
 -------------------------
 * Fixed bug if gotcha.library is not present in libs:
 * Fixed bug if banner file cannot be opened/found
 * Portreqester for ARexxSender now opens on public screens too, same for
   GFreq and GPoll windows.
 * Added backslash to escape characters for GList
 * Changed user login. Now acts like TD: Automatic banner and SPAWNMESSAGE
   display after a few seconds. Banner is shown earlier.
 * Added UPDATE option to GList, no longer need to compile the whole nodelist
   if only a password, setconfig, dial, cost config changed.
 * Fixed crash if owndevunit.library is not present and serial device cannot
   be allocated/opened.
 * Added DisplayBeep() if connecting.
 * Added CONFIG keyword to GList.


 version v1.0
 ------------
 first public release.
@endnode

